 Patensie or in the Gamtoos River Valley cannot deliver his fruit to a packing facility outside the valley, }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\b\loch\b except for economic considerations such as transport costs}{\ltrch\dbch. The respondent made this submission in support of a broader market \'96 the whole of South 
